survey.name: tag
survey.constraint: (function() { if (data('tag')!=2){return true;} alert('Fix Tag Number'); return false;})()

survey.name: crown_ratio
survey.constraint: (function() { if (data('crown_ratio') <= 100  && data('crown_ratio') >=1){return true;} alert('Crown Ratio Needs to be Fixed'); return false;})()

prompt.text: Crown Ratio must be between 1 and 100

survey.name: lean_angle
survey.constraint: (function() { if (data('lean_angle') <= 120  && data('lean_angle') >=0){return true;} alert('Lean Angle Needs to be Fixed'); return false;})()

prompt.text: Lean Angle must be between 0 and 120

survey.name: crown_percentage
survey.constraint: (function() { if (data('crown_percentage') <= 100  && data('crown_percentage') >=0){return true;} alert('Crown Ratio Needs to be Fixed'); return false;})()

prompt.text: Crown Percentage must be between 0 and 100

survey.name: tree_percentage
survey.constraint: (function() { if (data('tree_percentage') <= 100  && data('tree_percentage') >=0){return true;} alert('Tree Percentage Needs to be Fixed'); return false;})()

prompt.text: Tree Percentage must be between 0 and 100

survey.name: distance
survey.constraint: (function() { if (data('distance') <= 25.0  && data('distance') >=0.1){return true;} alert('Distance Needs to be Fixed'); return false;})()

survey.name: azimuth
survey.constraint: (function() { if (data('azimuth') <= 360  && data('azimuth') >=0){return true;} alert('Azimuth Range needs to be fixed'); return false;})()

prompt.text: Azimuth value must be between 0 and 360
